Package cscie55.project

Main package with solution for final project in class CSCI E-55, Fall 2013.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ATM
    ATM interface that contains the methods to be used between client and server in the ATM distributed application using Java RMI.
    ATMFactory
    ATMFactory is a class that returns ATM stubs to be used by the server process to attend different client processes.
    ATMListener
    Equips the Client to receive TransactionNotification messages from the ATM.
    Bank
    Bank interface that contains the methods that the Bank remote object is capable of doing.
    Security
    Remote interface that has methods for authenticating AccountInfo objects and for authorizing specific operations on individual accounts.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    Class that represents one account in the ATM Distributed Application using Java RMI.
    AccountInfo
    AccountInfo is a class that includes information to identify an Account in our distributed application.
    ATMAuthentication
    ATMAuthentication is a class whose instances represent each of the authorized (accountNumber, pin) pairs that are available as bank accounts.
    ATMAuthorization
    ATMAuthorization is a class whose instances indicate each of the permitted Commands for a given account's number.
    ATMFactoryImpl
    RMI-ready implementation of the ATMFactory interface.
    ATMImpl
    ATMImpl class that implements the ATM interface on the server side.
    ATMServer
    The ATMServer class starts up and registers the ATMFactory with the RMI registry.
    BankImpl
    BankImpl implements the Bank interface on the server side of our distributed application.
    BankServer
    The BankServer class starts up and creates a Bank instance and a Security instance and registers each of them with the RMI Registry.
    Client
    Class that remotely invokes the ATMServer's methods.
    SecurityImpl
    Implements the methods of the Security interface.
    TransactionNotification
    TransactionNotification is a class that includes pertinent information about a particular transaction including target accounts and amounts.
